    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "##Download and Load\n",
        "\n",
        "SWOT files are stored as NetCDF4/HDF5 files. Because satellite swaths follow a curved orbital path, their internal grids are not simple squares; we will load the file natively using xarray."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "utdhtrIcIiRz"
